title: Resist Temptation | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Resist Temptation | Joel Osteen
description:
To live a life of freedom, you have to realize you can’t overcome every temptation on your own. Let God equip you with the strength you need to walk in victory!

 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
